---
title: Paprika-Rubbed Chicken with Barley, Tomato and Avocado Salad
description: Sometimes it’s the simplest of combinations that are the most satisfying. This hearty barley salad is full of crunchy cucumber, juicy tomatoes, and creamy avocado. A touch of olive oil and sherry vinegar are all it needs to shine. Perfectly seasoned, perfectly seared chicken seals the deal.
